text: @UPSHelp My package shows 2 different delivery addresses. One my address, and the other a drop off point. However, I called yesterday and spent 2 hours on the phone with you guys saying it can't be delievered to the drop off point. Also I took the day off work to be here to sign

@UPSHelp then the truck drove right past my house. Oh and been on the phone just trying to reach you guys for help. Is there a person that can actually tell me what's happening with my package? Because I got transferred from 2-3 different departments and nobody said the same

@UPSHelp  So after spending 2 hrs yesterday, talking to 3 people (2 "customer service", & 1 tech) I get told the package will be delivered to my home Spend 30+ mins on phone today 2 get told it will be delivered to the drop off point. I took the day off! #UPShatesme #UPSscrewedme
